{"tid":2179812,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"《大公報》指控與台灣牧師助青年赴台 朱耀明斥捏造事實","createTime":"2020-08-29T11:39:37.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-29T12:26:45.000Z","uid":240362,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"dffd0fe826c573bdbd2fc76023d432a7f2745b14","tid":2179812,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-29T11:39:37.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200829/JPAQ2MSWWZFZLDNX4WFYYZNQPM/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200829%2FJPAQ2MSWWZFZLDNX4WFYYZNQPM%2F&d=aJB%2Bq6ruafnyRbkwc%2FW5Zq7%2FPCTF2%2B9SGuy7I2Db2XM%3D&h=a18a1fa9\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200829%2FJPAQ2MSWWZFZLDNX4WFYYZNQPM%2F&h=279ff7c8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200829/JPAQ2MSWWZFZLDNX4WFYYZNQPM/</a><br />\n<br />\n12名因涉反修例運動被捕的青年日前乘船欲偷渡往台灣，惟途中遭廣東海警截獲拘捕，中共喉舌《大公報》今天（29日）指控，台北濟南基督長老教會主任牧師黃春生替「暴徒」潛逃台灣，更指黃與曾發起佔中的朱耀明牧師相熟。朱耀明發聲明指，全篇報道涉及他的內容完全失實，直指自己並不認識黃春生牧師，未曾與對方見面或聯繫，他亦無參與抗爭青年的逃亡安排。對《大公報》捏造事實和惡意暗示，朱耀明表示憤怒，並保留採取法律行動的權利。"},{"pid":"0501ab55c7edbfbc3d01f252527b999704834f49","tid":2179812,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-29T12:00:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5f5e732b254aadce5eeb084c72fc3acf66d76b9d","tid":2179812,"uid":199771,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-29T12:26:45.000Z","msg":"黎智英 的僕人<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/RGwjoit.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRGwjoit.jpg&h=49ba7db4&s={SIZE}\"